# Customer Product EDA Analysis

## Project Overview

This project performs Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) using customer and product datasets.

The analysis was conducted using Python in Jupyter Notebook.

## Objectives

- Calculate total inventory value
- Analyze product discounts
- Count total products
- Filter customers by city and country
- Visualize top purchasing cities
- Analyze product purchase trends
- Generate customer purchase reports

## Tools Used

- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Jupyter Notebook

## Key Findings

- Total Inventory Value: 13,133,737.88
- Total Products: 100
- 67 purchases involved discounted products
- Most purchased products:
  - Half
  - Own
  - Every

